# Executive Summary

Jopetnah International Limited is a diversified international conglomerate and social enterprise committed to delivering integrated, innovative, and sustainable solutions that create measurable value for businesses, governments, development partners, institutions, and communities.

Founded in 2016 and headquartered in Kampala, Uganda, the company has grown into a multidisciplinary organization operating across sixteen strategic sectors. Our integrated business model enables clients to access a broad portfolio of professional services through one trusted corporate partner, simplifying project delivery while promoting efficiency, innovation, and long-term value creation.

Our expertise spans strategic consultancy and advisory, research and development, engineering and construction, healthcare and pharmaceuticals, transport and logistics, tourism and hospitality, education, agribusiness, technology, renewable energy, marketing, international recruitment, natural resources, events management, FMCG, and international trade.

By integrating technical excellence with strategic thinking, Jopetnah International Limited develops solutions that strengthen institutions, improve operational performance, accelerate sustainable growth, and contribute to economic transformation.

Our growing regional and international network positions us to connect opportunities across Africa and the global marketplace while maintaining a strong commitment to responsible business practices, innovation, transparency, and stakeholder value.

As we continue expanding our capabilities and partnerships, we remain focused on our purpose of empowering businesses worldwide through knowledge, collaboration, and sustainable development.

